text: Jelena Vujičić (; born 24 January 2001) is a Montenegrin alpine skier. She competed in slalom and giant slalom at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Montenegrin female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Montenegro Category:Alpine skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics
